				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Requirments to be an EV mage:
<br />

<br />
Raid times, rules, and probation
<br />
-------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
Raid times are currently 5 days a week with Thursday and Sunday as days off. Raids start at ~6 pm CST~ and may last up to 11:00pm or 12:00am CST depending on the raid and target. (this is subject to change)
<br />

<br />
You MUST maintain 50% attendance or better to pass probabtion. Probation will last 30 days.  When joining EV you have decieded to be the best at what you do and raid hardcore. Attending raids is mandatory while online during the posted raid hours.
<br />

<br />
Gear, Flags, and AAs
<br />
------------------------
<br />

<br />
Gear req:
<br />
~You Must have atleast 3000 hp / 5000 mana.
<br />

<br />
~You Must have atleast 150 Cold resist, Fire resist, and Magic resist. Poison and Disease should be close to that as well. 
<br />

<br />
~You Must have 1 Right click item. (2 is a bonus)
<br />

<br />
~Having more than a few Flowing thought is also a bonus.
<br />

<br />
flag req:
<br />
~We are not going to reflag any mages for elemental planes. If you join EV and you happen to be missing a flag that will unlock Elemental planes dont expect to get it. Occasionally we may do some back flags, but currently we are only looking for elemental planes enabled mages. If this isnt you do not be discouraged some exceptions may be made depending on who is applying. 
<br />

<br />
~Having Earth B key is a STRONG +
<br />

<br />
AA Abilities:
<br />
~You must have between 150 - 200 AAs. No Exceptions.
<br />

<br />
recommended skills,
<br />

<br />
RS3
<br />
Regen3
<br />
SCF3
<br />
SCM3
<br />
MC3
<br />
ND3
<br />
Pet Hold &lt;Required&gt;
<br />
FBO
<br />
Waterform 3
<br />
PP5
<br />
IE5
<br />
HoE3
<br />
SM2
<br />
FoM3
<br />
*if you dont know what these abreviations are, DO NOT apply.
<br />
Having full pet LoH ability is a bonus as well.
<br />

<br />
Finally some personal notes:
<br />

<br />
Elitists and Vagrants have the best magicians on the server. I will NOT settle for anything less. Upon joining you will always be tested to make sure you maintain a level of 100% play ability. If you do not have the foresight to manage your skills effeciently throughout a raid do not apply. If you get discouraged after Failing a target 10 times and refuse to go for 11 then dont apply.
<br />

<br />
Being an EV mage is an honor. We stick together, we help eachother, and we grow better from one another. If you cant handle that then dont apply. It is tough to become an EV mage, however; if you are serious about joining and think you can handle being in our ranks then you wont find a better home. 
<br />

<br />
We look forward to meeting you,
<br />

<br />
Xinben Stiltskin</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
